# GRAVITY GRAB SCENE
# Zero-G orbital platform · deep space backdrop
# Camera: wide FOV 70° · tracks orb cluster centroid
# Lighting: 2x cold blue fills · star background skybox
# Orb spawner volumes fill circular arena
# Arena boundary = invisible sphere force field (radius 12)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

